&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an independent and analytical FP&amp;amp;A Manager to join our Financial Planning &amp;amp; Analysis (FP&amp;amp;A) team. This critical role will partner closely with key budget owners in our Technology Centers and Core Labs, driving the annual budgeting process, project-specific forecasting, and strategic decision-making. The ideal candidate will possess a strong foundation in financial modeling, experience at a science organization, and a proven ability to translate data into actionable insights for leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
