&lt;li&gt;Develop scenario-driven financial models for key Institute Initiatives, new scientific programs, and capital expenditures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive continuous improvement in FP&amp;amp;A processes, reporting automation, and financial system utilization (e.g., Netsuite, Prendio).&lt;/li&gt;
