&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://arcinstitute.org/labs/zhoulab&quot;&gt;Zhou Lab&lt;/a&gt; is looking for motivated, hard-working and curious applicants. Our expertise is in single-cell epigenomic modeling. We use high-throughput single-cell multiomic technologies and build computational models to study spatiotemporal dynamics of gene regulation.&lt;/p&gt;
