&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are highly motivated and passionate about applying cutting-edge functional genomics techniques to enable scientific discoveries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are diligent, detail oriented, adaptable, and excel at troubleshooting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are committed to generating high quality data and maintaining good documentation practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy working collaboratively with others and thrive in a fast-paced, dynamic work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You respect the process and are comfortable carrying out the routine execution of tasks while identifying opportunities to troubleshoot and address bottlenecks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt

