&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take pride in producing consistent, high-quality results on a predictable schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are diligent, meticulous, and committed to thorough documentation and good record-keeping practices.&lt;/li&gt;
